### Step 1: Presigned URL 발급
POST http://localhost:8080/api/products/images/upload-url
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "imageType": "THUMBNAIL",
  "contentType": "image/png",
  "contentLength": 69,
  "originalFileName": "test.png"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("uploadUrl", response.body.uploadUrl);
%}

### Step 2: Presigned URL로 MinIO에 직접 업로드 (PUT)
# Content-Type은 Step 1에서 지정한 값과 반드시 일치해야 함
PUT {{uploadUrl}}
Content-Type: image/png

< ./test.png